Hull strawberries and cut in half; place in a stainless steel saucepan. Combine SPLENDA(R) Granulated Sweetener and pectin in a small mixing bowl; add to strawberries and toss until coated. Bring to a boil over medium heat; reduce heat and simmer 4-5 minutes. Remove from heat; stir in lime peel and juice. Chill, covered. Keeps 7-10 days.